<h2 class="h3">Recent publications</h2>

<p><strong><a href="https://www.health.govt.nz/publication/mental-health-and-wellbeing-year-review">Mental Health Quarter Three&nbsp;(Jan-Mar&nbsp;2021) Progress Update</a></strong></p>

<p class="rtecenter"><a href="https://www.health.govt.nz/publication/mental-health-and-wellbeing-year-review"><img alt="The year in review: Quarter 2 update" class="figure-border" height="208" src="../sites/default/files/images/quarterly-update-q3-2020-2021.jpg" style="margin-bottom: 0;" width="150" /></a></p>

<p>This document outlines the third quarter (January to March 2021)&nbsp;progress made by the Ministry of Health on implementing He Ara Oranga.</p>

<hr />
<p><strong><a href="https://www.health.govt.nz/publication/covid-19-psychosocial-and-mental-wellbeing-plan">COVID-19 Psychosocial and Mental Wellbeing Plan</a></strong></p>

<p class="image-center"><a href="https://www.health.govt.nz/publication/covid-19-psychosocial-and-mental-wellbeing-plan"><img alt="COVID-19 Psychosocial and Mental Wellbeing Plan" class="figure-border" height="184" src="../sites/default/files/images/publications/kiakaha-coverdec2020.jpg" style="margin-bottom: 0;" width="130" /></a></p>

<p>A framework for actions to support the mental wellbeing of New Zealanders as we respond to the impacts of COVID-19.</p>

